Title: 031: AB Testing, Kissmetrics and Ways to a Better Lifestyle with David Tanaskovic
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with my good friend and a Director of a media marketing agency David Tanaskovic. You will cover of the tools that are used in the marketing space, talk about Kissmetrics, discuss how David views AB Testing and learn tips on how to have a better lifestyle.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/31
